  "body": "**Is your feature request related to a problem? Please describe.**\r\n\r\nWe would like to implement various features surrounding the weak subjectivity state.\r\nIn order to do so, we need to implement a few core utility functions, possibly just 1 to begin.\r\n\r\n**Describe the solution you'd like**\r\n\r\nImplement `get_latest_weak_subjectivity_checkpoint_epoch` as described here:\r\nhttps://notes.ethereum.org/@adiasg/weak-subjectvity-eth2#Distributing-Weak-Subjectivity-Checkpoint-States\r\n\r\nIdeally we would implement twice, once for `allForks.BeaconState`, and another for `CachedBeaconState<allForks.BeaconState>`.\r\n\r\nThe code can likely live in `packages/beacon-state-transition/src/util/weakSubjectivity.ts` and\r\n `packages/beacon-state-transition/src/fast/util/weakSubjectivity.ts`\r\n\r\n",
